  "title": "Wholesale Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Coordinate Wholesale centre’s and its warehouse daily operation and fulfilment</li><li>Multi-channel sales enquiries and quotation handling via phone, whatsapp and email without sale target</li><li>Liaise with warehouse and logistic staff to prepare customers’ orders and arrange delivery</li><li>Daily consolidation, settlement and cash deposit</li><li>Manage account receivable</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum GCE “O” level or equivalent.</li><li>Willing to work on alternate Saturday from 0830 to 1730hrs.</li><li>Relevant Aircon Sales experience is an advantage.</li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Basic MS Word, MS Outlook and MS Powerpoint skills.</li></ul><p><strong>Key selling points</strong></p><ul><li>Annual Wage Increment</li><li>Staff Purchase Discount</li><li>Have OT claim</li></ul>",
